tools: sys.write, sys.read, sys.download, sys.find
tools: github.com/gptscript-ai/browser
model: gpt-3.5-turbo
args: url: Link to the article or page
args: dir: Directory to save the created files to



1. Browse to ${url} amd read the page contents
2. Create a tdlr text version of it for an Instagram reel or a tiktok video.max 100 words and no emojis
3. Split the text into 3 parts,save the texts to "${dir}/story-${INDEX}.txt"